{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_01","textHome":"在这颗地球的所有地方闪闪发光的、各种各样@领域的一等星们！正是为了目击你们的姿态@、聆听你们的话语、将你们的出色之处遍及@世界，我枇枇木巡才存在于此！然后，今天@我锁定的，就是那边的你！让我彻底感受一@下一等星的光辉吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":304200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":304200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_17","textHome":"OKOK，如果发生了难受的事情，逃避掉就@好了！我经常这么干哦！因为，虽然挑战和@忍耐都很重要，但回避也是很重要的吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":304200,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_18","textHome":"在实现了愿望的人之中，也有些人对于实现愿@望保持否定态度。但是，我不会否定哦！如@果能紧紧抓住，我是绝对会去拿到的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":400}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_19","textHome":"不知第多少次的表彰仪式！这次出现的，会是@什么样的大奖呢——！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":400}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_20","textHome":"刚才，从天上降下了声音……！我是不是觉醒@了什么技能！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_21","textHome":"真的连犹豫都完全不会犹豫，要说的话就像丝@线一样嗖嗖地跳出来了！这就是进入了领域@的感觉吧！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304200,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_22","textHome":"我枇枇木巡可是几乎不知沉默为何物！在从天@而降的话语中传达的、战斗者们的目的地，@到底有什么呢！对巧妙话语的感动！？对展@现了勇姿之人的感动！？不，一定是这两者@交织而成的最棒的情感吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":304200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"id":304200,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_23","textHome":"对我不断疯狂抗议“太吵了”的听众们，总有@一天也会变得听不见我的声音就会感到美中@不足吧！所以，放心地收听吧！要开始了哦@！今年的我也一定是解说员中的风云人物吧@！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":304200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_24","textHome":"跑向这里的是巡选手！现在正是她能否赶上约@定时间的紧要关头！勉强冲线——！哈……@哈……让你久等了！！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":304200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_25","textHome":"鸡蛋破了……鸡蛋掉了下去！在煎锅和鸡蛋奏@响的协奏曲中加入培根的香味，制成的正是@……早、早饭！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":304200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":1}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_26","textHome":"嗯？我只是在看着你哦？毕竟被解说的话饭会@难以下咽，而且之前你已经发了大火……我@只是觉得要是变成那样，就连话也说不上了@……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304200,"motion":1}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_02","textHome":"看见了！你正是未来的最佳·魔法少女！就让@我，著名主持人枇枇木巡，解说一番你的人@生吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_27","textHome":"好了，在放学之后为您带来的是水火不容的足@球社和棒球社之间的篮球比赛！！虽然保证@了公平性，但这到底是怎么回事啊！！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_28","textHome":"大家都在听吗——？在夜间为您带来的，是魔@法少女和魔女之间的战斗！啊，哇哇！要是@往这边攻击过来，我岂不是就解说不成了吗@！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":400}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_29","textHome":"诶嘿嘿，虽然巡是个很能制造麻烦的吵吵闹闹@的MC，但是别看这样，我也是被各方面争@来抢去的大红人哦～"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_30","textHome":"怎怎、怎么会！居然在没有同伴的时间点探测@到魔女的反应！明明一边战斗一边解说很困@难的！不，说到底就没有听众吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.4,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_31","textHome":"莫非，马上就要开始了吗！？在无尽镜界举行@的特别活动！那就该我出场了！这次，我也@会将大家的勇姿转播到您的身边！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":1}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_32","textHome":"这就是预料之外的大混战吗！？魔法少女之间@的争斗居然发展到这么大的规模实在是很凄@惨，但我枇枇木巡会同时为您解说双方战况@的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":304200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_33","textHome":"我在这个笔记本里，总结了自己在电视和收音@机里听到的在意的台词。顺带一提，也有学@生们说的话哦。毕竟偶尔还是会出点金句的@嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":304200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":304200,"motion":300}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3042_00_34","textHome":"我接下来正好打算去游戏厅！当然不是作为玩@家，而是去担任解说的工作哦？如果你也要@参加的话，就尽管期待吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":304200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":200}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":304200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voi